Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:05.35,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she can do maths in her head?{Probably wrong, I'm hearing 安産}{close, it's 暗算}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:06.56,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:08.32,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about Nano-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:16.63,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's a robot, don't you think she might have robotic features?{alternatively, "robot-like"}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:18.06,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:19.41,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she's a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:22.41,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,But she has a key on her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:26.41,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You think she's a robot just because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:27.54,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:31.46,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,No, but think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:32.38,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:34.72,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:35.93,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Like, honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:37.29,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,isn't it amazing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:38.08,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reasoning behind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:43.73,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I want to investigate to see if Nano-chan is a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.56,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,No, you shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:47.14,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:49.02,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.22,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Nano-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:22.77,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:24.95,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:30.67,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,What is 3260 plus 260 divided by 320? {Math lesson time~ This is 3260+(260/320) because of order of operations. However, I'm preeeeeetty sure that the intention on this line was (3260 + 260)/320 as can be seen three lines later. This is especially true since the second statement gives an answer of 11, while the prior gives an answer of 3260.8125 - Caly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:31.08,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.19,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:37.30,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Three-thousand two-hundred and sixty plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:40.03,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,If it's too hard for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:42.05,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,You can use your features.{Have we been using the term "features"? I can't remember.}{機能 - functions, leaving features as the meaning is the same, kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.25,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yukko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.47,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.60,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:51.06,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.32,Default,Yukko+Mio,0000,0000,0000,,It's an abacus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:55.95,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.36,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Start by clearing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.32,Default,Yukko+Mio,0000,0000,0000,,How basic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:04.08,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.83,Default,Yukko+Mio,0000,0000,0000,,She's a b-beginner!{they really stutter the "b" in "beginner".}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.54,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Three-thousand two-hundred and sixty plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:14.29,Default,Yukko+Mio,0000,0000,0000,,She's not using the abacus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.38,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yukko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:17.66,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Aioi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:18.51,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:20.67,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:23.48,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that was a correct answer in various ways...{Remember, she's a comedian at heart.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:24.24,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you she's not a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:30.18,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.21,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.07,Default,Mio+Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Could it possibly be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.74,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.53,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.12,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Oil has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.70,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,It's soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:50.82,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yukko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:54.09,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:56.97,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Minakami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.17,Default,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.40,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,She threw a fastball!{euphemism for "getting straight to the point"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.72,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:08.56,Default,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:11.55,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:12.81,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.44,Default,Mio+Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,She'll drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.94,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,It was a miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.07,Default,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to have this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:29.91,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,A curveball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.62,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,A monkey wrench!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.42,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.33,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,She'll eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.83,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,It was a miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:44.72,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two should cut this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.72,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You're troubling Nano-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.22,Default,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,It's skinship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:51.93,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just wanted to become friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:52.93,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a step in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:57.97,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.68,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.90,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.42,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:07.70,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Since you don't need this soup, I'll drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.12,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,See? Nano-chan says so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.22,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.93,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Did my crown come off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:15.70,Default-Alt,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Put yourself in Nano-chan's shoes and think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.12,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:59.12,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,How are they able to make something of such high quality?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:03.71,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Shinonome Nano, who transferred here the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.92,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Her existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.79,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that key...{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.01,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at her, she is a robot.{She has to be a robot.}{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:16.55,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Why hasn't she been shown to the scientific community?{Passive voice}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:20.71,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she attending this school as if it isn't a big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.65,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,I want to research.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.61,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,I want to research her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:29.80,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to make her mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:36.79,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nakamura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.83,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I brought the books you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.14,Default,Nakamrua,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:45.69,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, I'll excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.30,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Shinonome, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.68,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:53.35,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I don't want to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:56.15,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make excuses like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.18,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,I was just making some.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.81,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,It's a thank you for bringing me the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.94,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Just drink some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:05.52,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, just one cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:10.04,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll test whether or not sleeping medicine works on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:15.73,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,If that doesn't work, I'll use the "Short Circuit-kun" that I created yesterday on her from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.69,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Here, drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.77,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.76,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,I drank it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.35,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,I must endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.55,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,I must endure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.82,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll excuse myself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.45,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:57.03,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Use Short Circuit-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.87,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Short Circuit-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.00,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.39,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the science teacher, Nakamura, fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:09.71,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,She sure faints a lot. Nakamura, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.31,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,That was pretty close today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:28.32,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,But Aioi-san and Minakami-san seem like really good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:31.42,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they could become my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.18,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.45,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.81,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the maximum power of a rocket punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:56.11,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:57.93,Default-Alt,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nano, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:00.31,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nano, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:03.60,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why did you say it twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:07.55,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:10.82,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,can you hurry up and take this off of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:13.87,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:15.02,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.70,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's hard for me to sit in a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.01,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone looks at me like I'm strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:22.50,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,and on top of that, I was recorded on video.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:25.69,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I had to try to cover it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.69,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,But it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:33.30,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,But people won't treat me like a\Nnormal girl if I have this key attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:35.09,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,You'll definitely get popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.88,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:40.55,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to live a normal school life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.50,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you put a weapon like this on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.34,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it didn't come out at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.80,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you want people to find out you're a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:23.51,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,It's obviously because robots aren't cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.02,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Robots are cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:29.02,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,They are not cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.40,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,They're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.86,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,This gun is, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:32.98,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.70,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,The toe USB, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:36.36,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.07,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sweets coming out of my forehead, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.95,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.02,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, you're a mad professor!{MADDO SCIENTISUTO}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.58,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:50.60,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be more normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.23,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's a chikuwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.23,Note,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Chikuwa is a tube-shaped fish cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.74,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Chikuwa sure is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.27,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.12,Default,Daifuku,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we have daihuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're cheap! {Rice cake or Daifuku..}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.93,Default,Daifuku,0000,0000,0000,,It's daihuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:23.85,Default,Daifuku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nakanajou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.02,Default,Nakanajou,0000,0000,0000,,Daihuku don't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.43,Default,Daifuku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:46.53,Default,Daifuku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing this half-heartedly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.28,Default,Daifuku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting my life on the lin{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.29,Default,Nakanajou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me say it so many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:00.05,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I failed last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.92,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,The sleeping medicine scheme was badly thought out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.81,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she is a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:08.30,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,She probably won't lose consciousness without a really powerful hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.03,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,And that's where this comes in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.69,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to test it out before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:14.23,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,For use against robots, Short Circuit-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.82,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Using this, I can knock her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.05,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'll finally capture her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.90,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:56.39,Default,Nakamura,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.44,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nakamura-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:07.45,Default,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you can't leave your top button undone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:09.30,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. You're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.95,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it if I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:11.82,Default,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look like it, but I'm actually in charge of student guidance!{consistency check, please, what term did we use for this before?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.26,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get that position?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:17.44,Default,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:20.25,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.56,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:24.34,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:27.05,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?{alt: "dafuq" - kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.85,Default,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mako-chan, you can't fix it yourself, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.64,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You really are annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.16,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,"Mako-chan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:36.93,Default,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.56,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.90,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.17,Default,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll button it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:47.86,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,"You"? "Button it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:51.41,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hang around me at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.50,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,H... "Hang around"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.67,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of relationship do they have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.04,Default-Alt,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,See? It came off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.93,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That's just perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.57,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have stuff to do, so bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:09.41,Default,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:12.18,Default,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be laughed at if you look sloppy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.14,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.68,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You're always sloppy at home, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.56,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,At home!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:21.81,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sloppy-looking!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.73,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sloppy-looking, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.00,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I an idiot for getting excited like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.06,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,And why is a Chinese dress sloppy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.06,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a normal sloppy-looking appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:34.21,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,What am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.48,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,I should be ashamed as a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:38.66,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,A normal sloppy-looking appearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.67,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sloppy-looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.54,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.50,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's good enough, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:47.79,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:49.92,Default,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about the button?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:53.93,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Oguri Cap is like this!{Cpt. Oguri - Mai's dog - kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.65,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.00,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.62,Default,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about the button?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.24,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.24,Default,Annaka,0000,0000,0000,,Takasaki-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:21.37,Default,Annaka,0000,0000,0000,,Nakanojou-kun passed out in the science room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:25.67,Default,Annaka,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to come immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:25.67,Default-Alt,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:26.59,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:36.15,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:37.76,Default,Annaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.66,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Nakanojou hasn't passed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.86,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might just be taking a nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.78,Default,Annaka,0000,0000,0000,,But his eyes have gone completely white!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.15,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Draw them in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:55.49,Default,Annaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:16:59.11,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:03.91,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is going on there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:07.13,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Watching out for illicit relationships is more important than someone passing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:11.00,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's an educator's... Um, well, what it means to be an educator!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.72,Default,Annaka,0000,0000,0000,,That's Sakurai-sensei's younger brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:15.43,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.26,Default,Annaka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.14,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Here it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.14,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hurry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:28.39,Default,Takasaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's what being a teacher is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.44,Default,Annaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:11.39,Default,Bus,0000,0000,0000,,Next stop: Kokusadame Station, north entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:15.24,Default,Bus,0000,0000,0000,,The bus will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.78,Default,BrownHair,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're not getting off there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.45,Default,BlackHair,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to press the button.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.58,Default,BrownHair,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you press it earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.20,Default,BlackHair,0000,0000,0000,,Someone got off then, so it was fine in the end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.48,Default,BrownHair,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So it's like helping someone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.47,Default,BlackHair,0000,0000,0000,,See? Someone got off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:31.77,Default,BrownHair,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:40.30,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mum, do we have a tear-off calendar?{"daily calendar", isn't it?}{it's either a tear-off calendar, a daily calendar or a block calendar as well - kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.01,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there one in the cupboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.99,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Professor! Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:00.24,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nano. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:04.54,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please just remove this key?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:07.70,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,It causes so many problems for school life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:12.60,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,For the high jump, all I could do was a belly roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:15.84,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I got called off-sides in soccer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.92,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,It can be taken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:24.51,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me earlier if it could be taken off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:25.88,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it off right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:31.21,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Every day of youth is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:35.72,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I can finally live as a normal high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:38.99,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please hurry and take it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:43.64,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:44.70,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Could it possibly be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.08,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,I took it.{PUN - I TOOK a photo of it}{TL Note: "toru" means "to take off" as in to remove, but also "to take" as in a photo.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.08,Note,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: "Toru" means "to take off" as in to remove, but also "to take" as in a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.04,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:54.33,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't make stupid jokes like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:56.42,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.{she says it in a cute way.. "Sowwy, sowwy." - kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.88,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,So, can this key be removed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:00.48,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:11.20,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any more stupid jokes!{she says old jokes, not stupid. - kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.94,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,So, can you take it off or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:14.79,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:19.68,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken lots of keys before.{off?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours can be easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:22.62,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:24.41,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Coin! Coin! Coin! Zoom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:29.38,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,You went "Coin! Coin! Coin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:31.66,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you went "Z-Zoom!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.79,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:37.55,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,My breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.94,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.26,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,I laughed too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:45.45,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, I've been having really unnatural reactions all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:49.15,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Have you done anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:49.81,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,To me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.97,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, yesterday, I added a reaction feature to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:21:00.04,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of messed up feature is that supposed to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:01.53,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you add a feature like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.15,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Because it seemed funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.88,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.20,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.00,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.21,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,If this continues, I'm going to die from these reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:18.04,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,See? Isn't it funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.04,Default-Alt,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,It's not funny at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:22.20,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, putting the key aside,{lit. "Professor, letting the key spin for later," - kb_z }
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:23.88,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,could you please remove this feature?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.72,Default,Professor,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be a hundred yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:22.90,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This is my maximum capacity.{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:28.41,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:30.01,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,I've been told that I'm slippery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:31.98,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm oil, so I can't really help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.98,0:23:34.23,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told that a lot by my boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:35.92,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the boss of Oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:38.52,Default-Alt,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode of Nichijou is episode 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:39.99,Default-Alt,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared.
